                            Our business is structured to best serve our customers – responding to their needs and delivering value to them. We have five customer-facing lines of business: BT Global Services, BT Business, BT Consumer, BT Wholesale and Openreach. They are supported by our internal service unit, BT Technology, Service &amp; Operations.
