                    <h3 class="h3 color-purple text-strong">BT Wholesale</h3>
                    <p class="text-base text-base--margin-small">BT Wholesale provides services in Great Britain to more than 1,400 communications providers.</p>
                    <div class="block-toggle-parent" style="height: 46px;">
                        <a class="module-block module-block--toggle h4" href="#collapsible-content-05" data-collapsible-toggle="" data-collapsible-accordion="" data-collapsible-text="Close" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapsible-4" style="height: 24px;">Read more</a>
